Who here doesn't know that?

260
00:21:00,018 --> 00:21:01,957
Watch your mouth.

261
00:21:01,957 --> 00:21:04,488
- Father isn't well. 
 - My point, exactly.

262
00:21:04,488 --> 00:21:08,498
Father is bedridden now. Nothing good will come out of people talking about it.

263
00:21:08,498 --> 00:21:12,027
Chang Je, I heard the politicians aren't keen on it, either.

264
00:21:12,027 --> 00:21:13,568
They say it violates the separation of banking and commerce.

265
00:21:13,568 --> 00:21:14,837
Yes, that's right.

266
00:21:14,837 --> 00:21:16,838
That's why Father said he wanted to support

267
00:21:16,838 --> 00:21:20,508
a presidential candidate who'd ease the rules of separation of banking and commerce.

268
00:21:20,508 --> 00:21:22,978
Then it would be resolved right away, I suppose.

269
00:21:22,978 --> 00:21:24,248
He asked you one question.

270
00:21:24,248 --> 00:21:27,848
Why ramble on, and spoil the mood?

271
00:21:28,618 --> 00:21:30,177
All right.

272
00:21:31,047 --> 00:21:32,487
My point is...

273
00:21:32,487 --> 00:21:35,787
Whether we want to push Cheongwadae or influence the National Assembly,

274
00:21:35,787 --> 00:21:38,758
we can't do it without Father.

275
00:21:38,758 --> 00:21:40,287
Am I wrong, Hyungnim Young Ki?

276
00:21:40,287 --> 00:21:42,127
- Mr. Lee. 
 - Yes, Sir.

277
00:21:42,127 --> 00:21:46,668
As for the board meeting, we will proceed as planned.

278
00:21:47,514 --> 00:21:48,409
Oppa Young Ki!

279
00:21:48,409 --> 00:21:54,186
We cannot leave Father's position vacant.

280
00:21:54,186 --> 00:21:56,337
I'll fill in for him.

281
00:22:08,086 --> 00:22:11,257
Hyungnim Young Ki, Father has blindsided you so many times.

282
00:22:11,257 --> 00:22:16,257
Do you still not get the picture? Are you dumb?

283
00:22:16,257 --> 00:22:19,328
He wants Do Jun to run the financial holding company.

284
00:22:19,328 --> 00:22:21,238
Do you not understand what that means?

285
00:22:21,238 --> 00:22:23,738
I bet you have no idea.

286
00:22:23,738 --> 00:22:28,377
He'll sponsor the presidential candidate who'd ease the regulations on the separation,

287
00:22:28,377 --> 00:22:30,278
so the head of the financial holding company

288
00:22:30,278 --> 00:22:32,778
could go on to rule the entire Soonyang Group. In other words, he has chosen

289
00:22:32,778 --> 00:22:35,578
that fool Yoon Ki's son, Do Jun, as his successor.

290
00:22:35,578 --> 00:22:38,618
You're so afraid of Father that you have nothing to your name.

291
00:22:38,618 --> 00:22:41,187
Now, you'll take what rightfully belongs to your son

292
00:22:41,187 --> 00:22:44,087
and put it in Do Jun's mouth?

293
00:22:44,087 --> 00:22:46,328
Aren't you too embarrassed to even face Seong Jun?

294
00:22:46,328 --> 00:22:47,457
That's enough, Uncle Dong Ki.

295
00:22:47,457 --> 00:22:49,897
You too! Get it together!

296
00:22:49,897 --> 00:22:51,897
Or you'll end up becoming a puppet like your father.

297
00:22:51,897 --> 00:22:53,939
What did you say?

298
00:22:54,598 --> 00:22:56,368
You little...

299
00:22:56,368 --> 00:22:59,037
Enough, both of you!

300
00:23:01,337 --> 00:23:04,507
Your father was right about you guys.

301
00:23:04,507 --> 00:23:10,585
I know I birthed you guys, but what is wrong with all of you?

302
00:23:10,585 --> 00:23:12,818
Knowing that your father is on the verge of dying,

303
00:23:12,818 --> 00:23:16,389
how dare you worry about what you might lose or gain first?

304
00:23:16,389 --> 00:23:18,329
Mom.

305
00:23:18,958 --> 00:23:21,728
I can't believe I have to see this.

306
00:23:21,728 --> 00:23:23,827
Calm down, Mother. You might faint at this rate.

307
00:23:23,827 --> 00:23:25,367
Forget it.

308
00:23:25,367 --> 00:23:27,498
Get out, all of you!

309
00:23:27,498 --> 00:23:29,637
I'm afraid your father would never wake up

310
00:23:29,637 --> 00:23:32,467
because he doesn't want to see the fools that you are!

311
00:23:32,467 --> 00:23:36,077
Why would you say that, Mom!

312
00:23:36,077 --> 00:23:38,508
Mom, go home and get some rest.

313
00:23:38,508 --> 00:23:41,447
We can't even see him anyway!

314
00:23:43,518 --> 00:23:44,817
Let's go home, Mother.

315
00:23:44,817 --> 00:23:49,788
I'm sure Do Jun's family will stay here anyway.

316
00:23:49,788 --> 00:23:52,941
You look so weary, Mother.

317
00:23:52,941 --> 00:23:56,598
We'll take you home. Let's go to Jeongsimjae, okay?

318
00:23:56,598 --> 00:23:57,998
Forget it.

319
00:23:57,998 --> 00:24:01,668
All my life, I've always stayed right by his side.

320
00:24:01,668 --> 00:24:04,868
He'll look for me the moment he wakes up.

321
00:24:07,546 --> 00:24:09,421
Heed my advice.

322
00:24:09,421 --> 00:24:11,377
Do not raise your voices in front of me again.

323
00:24:19,992 --> 00:24:24,428
Mother must still care for him very much, even at her age.

324
00:24:24,428 --> 00:24:27,067
Let's be honest. Without my mom's support,

325
00:24:27,067 --> 00:24:29,827
he wouldn't have been able to grow Soonyang into what it is today.

326
00:24:29,827 --> 00:24:31,398
No way.

327
00:24:31,398 --> 00:24:34,367
You should be good to me, too.

328
00:24:34,367 --> 00:24:35,968
Don't you remember what Mr. Baek said?

329
00:24:35,968 --> 00:24:39,738
In your fortune reading, you're blessed with rich parents first, and then a good wife.

330
00:24:39,738 --> 00:24:41,637
Mr. Baek is never wrong, you know.

331
00:24:41,637 --> 00:24:43,637
What do you think will happen with my father?

332
00:24:43,637 --> 00:24:45,778
Will he wake up?

333
00:24:45,778 --> 00:24:48,307
Yes, I believe so.

334
00:24:49,377 --> 00:24:50,947
What?

335
00:24:50,947 --> 00:24:52,988
- Will he wake up? 
 - Yes.

336
00:24:52,988 --> 00:24:54,617
According to his reading, he's extremely strong.

337
00:24:54,617 --> 00:24:56,557
He'll never succumb to accident injuries or illnesses.

338
00:24:56,557 --> 00:25:00,032
And he certainly won't pass away this year.

339
00:25:00,032 --> 00:25:02,428
Darn it, why...

340
00:25:02,428 --> 00:25:04,768
Why are you telling me this now?

341
00:25:04,768 --> 00:25:07,328
Because you asked me just now, Sir.

342
00:25:07,328 --> 00:25:08,797
Don't step in, Honey.

343
00:25:08,797 --> 00:25:10,867
Let them start the financial holding company or whatever.

344
00:25:10,867 --> 00:25:12,807
Just stay out of it.

345
00:25:12,807 --> 00:25:15,808
If Father wakes up, he'll be very angry.

346
00:25:15,808 --> 00:25:19,707
It's so easy for you to say. You have no idea how I feel right now.

347
00:25:19,707 --> 00:25:23,048
Mr. Baek, whom you trust so much, told me

348
00:25:23,048 --> 00:25:26,025
that once Do Jun survived a life-threatening incident,

349
00:25:26,025 --> 00:25:28,918
he'd become unbeatable...

350
00:25:28,918 --> 00:25:29,988
What was it?

351
00:25:29,988 --> 00:25:32,458
- Astronomical wealth... 
 - Yes!

352
00:25:32,458 --> 00:25:34,528
- What? 
 - Money will fall into his lap.

353
00:25:34,528 --> 00:25:37,258
That's right! Do I really have to

354
00:25:37,258 --> 00:25:41,968
let that lucky brat eat up the financial holding company too?

355
00:25:45,868 --> 00:25:47,708
Let me see.

356
00:26:21,607 --> 00:26:25,478
You have to attend the executive meeting in the morning.

357
00:26:44,027 --> 00:26:47,298
Just finish this and go to bed early, Father.

358
00:26:48,597 --> 00:26:51,367
Don't worry, Seong Jun.

359
00:26:52,208 --> 00:26:55,637
Your uncle is right.

360
00:26:57,577 --> 00:27:00,847
I will cancel the board meeting.

361
00:27:04,188 --> 00:27:06,795
I will go ahead and cancel the plan

362
00:27:07,448 --> 00:27:11,558
to establish the financial holding company.

363
00:27:11,558 --> 00:27:13,758
Father.

364
00:27:13,758 --> 00:27:18,998
I should have protected you.

365
00:27:21,537 --> 00:27:24,017
I'm too embarrassed even to face you.

366
00:27:32,648 --> 00:27:35,947
But earlier, I agreed with what you said.

367
00:27:37,918 --> 00:27:41,787
Follow Grandpa's wishes regarding the financial holding company.

368
00:27:42,918 --> 00:27:45,658
They might end up being his last wishes.

369
00:27:46,527 --> 00:27:53,097
You are his only rightful successor, Father.

370
00:28:10,417 --> 00:28:12,217
Sir, as per your instructions,

371
00:28:12,217 --> 00:28:15,417
the police have concluded that the truck driver was drunk

372
00:28:15,417 --> 00:28:17,457
and experienced brake issues, which caused the accident.

373
00:28:17,457 --> 00:28:19,887
They will go ahead and close the case.

374
00:28:19,887 --> 00:28:24,427
The police suspect the sedan that took off after the initial collision was a stolen vehicle.

375
00:28:24,427 --> 00:28:28,138
They're watching the CCTV footage to track it,

376
00:28:28,138 --> 00:28:30,468
but Mr. Woo thinks...

377
00:28:34,448 --> 00:28:38,273
since it was a highly elaborate accident, the car is probably already scrapped...

378
00:28:38,273 --> 00:28:39,978
Stop.

379
00:28:44,348 --> 00:28:46,248
You can stop there.

380
00:28:48,858 --> 00:28:52,831
We should tell Grandmother. She must be devastated.

381
00:28:52,831 --> 00:28:56,227
She's a speaker.

382
00:28:56,227 --> 00:29:00,998
Once she finds out, even Tom and Mary in New York will find out.

383
00:29:00,998 --> 00:29:04,798
Are you trying to mess it up?

384
00:29:06,868 --> 00:29:11,277
Warn Mr. Woo so that it won't leak.

385
00:29:11,277 --> 00:29:13,647
Yes, Sir. You don't need to worry.

386
00:29:13,647 --> 00:29:17,847
It won't only humiliate the family but put an end to Soonyang.

387
00:29:17,847 --> 00:29:22,258
How are we going to ask our clients and shareholders to trust us?

388
00:29:23,457 --> 00:29:30,687
Do you really think one of the three children planned this?

389
00:29:30,687 --> 00:29:32,868
The situation is evident.

390
00:29:32,868 --> 00:29:35,897
Mr. Yang has never caused even a minor accident since he started working for me.

391
00:29:35,897 --> 00:29:37,768
It wasn't even his first trip.

392
00:29:37,768 --> 00:29:42,138
Why on the way to the press conference of all times? Why that day, at that time?

393
00:29:43,377 --> 00:29:45,908
I can never give up on the financial holding company,

394
00:29:45,908 --> 00:29:49,518
and they'll never hand it over to Do Jun.

395
00:29:52,090 --> 00:29:54,288
The one who goes to the board meeting

396
00:29:54,288 --> 00:29:56,061
and stops the establishment

397
00:29:56,061 --> 00:29:59,542
of the holding company is the culprit of this accident.

398
00:29:59,542 --> 00:30:01,597
That's what I think.

399
00:30:01,597 --> 00:30:05,867
I'm going to the board meeting no matter what so I can see his face!

400
00:30:05,867 --> 00:30:10,898
When they see their father is fine, they will flip out.

401
00:30:11,710 --> 00:30:14,038
You'll be laughing in your sleep.

402
00:30:14,038 --> 00:30:16,677
This is a rare sight.

403
00:30:16,677 --> 00:30:20,848
Because it's me. Only Jin Yang Cheol can do this.

404
00:30:28,588 --> 00:30:31,487
He must be tired.

405
00:30:33,588 --> 00:30:36,857
I will come back tomorrow.

406
00:30:36,857 --> 00:30:39,327
Rest well, Chairman.

407
00:30:43,998 --> 00:30:45,808
Goodnight, Mr. Lee.

408
00:31:02,057 --> 00:31:06,687
Medical Director Jung told me you weren't well.

409
00:31:11,268 --> 00:31:14,828
Is that why you're rushing

410
00:31:15,640 --> 00:31:19,237
to establish the financial holding company,

411
00:31:19,237 --> 00:31:21,697
and leaving the Soonyang chairman position to me?

412
00:31:26,551 --> 00:31:33,266
As soon as you get up tomorrow, make a call

413
00:31:33,266 --> 00:31:35,757
to the press team in the PR Department.

414
00:31:36,818 --> 00:31:38,418
Okay?

415
00:31:39,157 --> 00:31:41,799
Look at this.

416
00:31:41,799 --> 00:31:45,527
The car is smashed into pieces,

417
00:31:45,527 --> 00:31:49,538
but no one is dead.

418
00:31:51,607 --> 00:31:54,878
That is Soonyang's car.

419
00:31:54,878 --> 00:31:58,337
Soonyang Motors.

420
00:32:00,108 --> 00:32:03,217
You know?

421
00:32:08,309 --> 00:32:12,327
I can't believe it was possible.

422
00:32:12,327 --> 00:32:14,588
It was possible.

423
00:32:21,897 --> 00:32:23,467
Okay, Grandfather.

424
00:32:23,467 --> 00:32:27,368
I'll call the press team to prepare the press release.

425
00:32:27,368 --> 00:32:31,877
Soonyang Motors' highest priority was safety.

426
00:32:31,877 --> 00:32:33,908
Behind it...

427
00:32:34,778 --> 00:32:38,448
was Chairman Jin Yang Cheol's struggle

428
00:32:38,448 --> 00:32:41,331
who never gave up

429
00:32:41,331 --> 00:32:45,132
despite inferiority in the market in the past ten years.

430
00:32:54,868 --> 00:32:57,437
You should go to sleep.

431
00:33:08,647 --> 00:33:10,248
Do Jun.

432
00:33:13,587 --> 00:33:16,987
Promise me

433
00:33:21,628 --> 00:33:24,157
that you'll be careful.

434
00:33:26,197 --> 00:33:28,568
Don't trust anyone.

435
00:33:37,208 --> 00:33:38,808
Okay.

436
00:33:40,578 --> 00:33:41,878
All right.

437
00:33:47,447 --> 00:33:48,887
Okay.

438
00:33:50,518 --> 00:33:52,557
You should get going.

439
00:33:58,898 --> 00:34:00,527
   

440
00:34:08,607 --> 00:34:10,408
Do Jun.

441
00:34:12,907 --> 00:34:14,678
Yes, Grandfather?

442
00:34:16,317 --> 00:34:20,778
Do you...still...

443
00:34:23,858 --> 00:34:26,827
want to buy Soonyang?

444
00:35:16,078 --> 00:35:19,708
Are you okay? Are you hurt a lot?

445
00:35:19,708 --> 00:35:21,708
Let me see.

446
00:35:27,188 --> 00:35:29,757
You should've told me if you were okay.

447
00:35:29,757 --> 00:35:33,458
I couldn't reach you all day. I was worried about you.

448
00:35:40,697 --> 00:35:45,437
It wasn't just an accident. Was it?

449
00:36:15,438 --> 00:36:17,267
Having trouble sleeping?

450
00:36:18,237 --> 00:36:21,367
Normally, you'd be in bed by now.

451
00:36:24,848 --> 00:36:27,507
I guess you're worried about Do Jun.

452
00:36:28,777 --> 00:36:32,148
The oldest daughter-in-law of Soonyang is different.

453
00:36:32,148 --> 00:36:35,157
You're too worried about your brother-in-law to sleep.

454
00:36:35,157 --> 00:36:38,657
Haven't you heard the doctor saying Do Jun was okay?

455
00:36:40,188 --> 00:36:44,757
That's why... I'm more worried.

456
00:36:47,368 --> 00:36:52,237
After the accident today, I thought Soonyang would be yours.

457
00:36:54,538 --> 00:36:56,477
Didn't you?

458
00:37:01,148 --> 00:37:08,977
I thought you couldn't sleep for that reason.

459
00:37:21,606 --> 00:37:24,398
Only a minor scratch on all passengers.

460
00:37:24,398 --> 00:37:27,837
Chairman Jin Yang Cheol is in a coma due to a car accident.

461
00:37:28,513 --> 00:37:31,107
Is it a scratch or a coma?

462
00:37:31,107 --> 00:37:33,947
What am I supposed to buy?

463
00:37:35,148 --> 00:37:36,947
There are only ten minutes left until the market opens.

464
00:37:36,947 --> 00:37:39,548
Will you keep a secret?

465
00:37:40,987 --> 00:37:44,657
What are you doing here? I thought you were in the hospital.

466
00:37:44,657 --> 00:37:46,987
I thought it was a big accident. Wait.

467
00:37:51,673 --> 00:37:53,173
What?

468
00:37:53,997 --> 00:37:55,998
Are you really okay?

469
00:37:55,998 --> 00:37:57,668
Oh, my dear CEO Oh.

470
00:37:59,377 --> 00:38:03,807
Then I'm buying 10,000 shares of Soonyang Motors today.

471
00:38:03,807 --> 00:38:06,748
Seriously. I'm disappointed.

472
00:38:10,355 --> 00:38:13,925
Don't forget that you promised me to keep your secret.

473
00:38:13,925 --> 00:38:19,087
The fact that they instigated the murder of their father, which was covered up as a car accident?

474
00:38:19,087 --> 00:38:23,268
Or how the father took the bait in an attempt to catch his kid?

475
00:38:23,268 --> 00:38:26,427
A secret or whatever, this is a crime.

476
00:38:26,427 --> 00:38:29,941
A secret or a crime, it'll all come to light on the day of the board meeting.

477
00:38:29,941 --> 00:38:33,974
Until then, I'll be at the hospital by Chairman Jin's side.

478
00:38:33,974 --> 00:38:36,714
So what am I to do?

479
00:38:37,507 --> 00:38:40,148
Soonyang Investment will call this meeting.

480
00:38:40,148 --> 00:38:42,847
The items will be the planning of making a holding company, and stockholders meeting for the board members.

481
00:38:42,847 --> 00:38:46,917
Please take up everything related to Soonyang Financial Holding Company.

482
00:38:46,917 --> 00:38:51,917
Is that why you put me here as the CEO as soon as we took over Soonyang Investment?

483
00:38:51,917 --> 00:38:54,958
Well, in the end, yes.

484
00:38:56,298 --> 00:38:59,928
Becoming the owner of Soonyang Financial Holding Company.

485
00:39:00,768 --> 00:39:03,037
Just as you wanted, Fellow Korean Lad.

486
00:39:03,037 --> 00:39:06,267
You'll soon have Soonyang Group in your hands.

487
00:39:11,307 --> 00:39:13,477
Are you sure about Father?

488
00:39:13,477 --> 00:39:17,518
You don't have to ask again. I heard it this morning from the police commissioner himself.

489
00:39:17,518 --> 00:39:20,148
The paramedic who was on the scene said

490
00:39:20,148 --> 00:39:24,287
he didn't suffer from any injuries like broken bones after that huge accident.

491
00:39:24,287 --> 00:39:26,458
Director Jung said he was in a coma.

492
00:39:26,458 --> 00:39:31,128
Even if what you said is true, why would he dare to lie against our family?

493
00:39:31,128 --> 00:39:34,268
   

494
00:39:34,268 --> 00:39:39,538
Father is testing us right now.

495
00:39:39,538 --> 00:39:40,608
Testing us?

496
00:39:40,608 --> 00:39:43,007
Everything came into the light with the financial holding company.

497
00:39:43,007 --> 00:39:45,008
The succession war has begun.

498
00:39:45,008 --> 00:39:46,108
So?

499
00:39:46,108 --> 00:39:49,507
While he has fallen asleep, and while nobody else can visit him here,

500
00:39:49,507 --> 00:39:52,248
he wants to see which one of you shows your devotion

501
00:39:52,248 --> 00:39:54,887
by coming in and visiting him every single day.

502
00:39:54,887 --> 00:39:58,988
It's a sort of loyalty test.

503
00:39:58,988 --> 00:40:00,988
- A loyalty test? 
 - Yes.

504
00:40:00,988 --> 00:40:03,598
- My father? 
 - Yes.

505
00:40:04,998 --> 00:40:06,298
Stop talking nonsense.

506
00:40:06,298 --> 00:40:08,737
Haven't you read "King Lear" by Shakespeare?

507
00:40:08,737 --> 00:40:10,697
Why do you think these are called the classics?

508
00:40:10,697 --> 00:40:13,608
I'm seeing through the essence of human nature now.

509
00:40:13,608 --> 00:40:16,507
You're so frustrating. Goodness.

510
00:40:16,507 --> 00:40:19,108
I need to see my father just once.

511
00:40:19,108 --> 00:40:22,648
I'm not trying to cross over to North Korea or visit the Moon.

512
00:40:22,648 --> 00:40:26,788
I just need to visit the ICU of this hospital once.

513
00:40:26,788 --> 00:40:29,418
- Oppa Dong Ki. 
 - Huh? What?

514
00:40:34,828 --> 00:40:40,227
I heard an odd rumor today, Director Jung.

515
00:40:40,227 --> 00:40:45,637
That Chairman Jin's body did not have any external injury from the accident.

516
00:40:45,637 --> 00:40:48,738
Can he still fall into a coma despite the lack of injury?

517
00:40:48,738 --> 00:40:50,378
Director Jung.

518
00:40:50,378 --> 00:40:55,177
