519
00:40:57,117 --> 00:40:59,048
Man.

520
00:40:59,048 --> 00:41:01,755
I finally get it.

521
00:41:01,755 --> 00:41:07,387
He's in a coma due to his chronic illness, cerebral arteriovenous malformation, right?

522
00:41:07,387 --> 00:41:08,827
Vice-Chairman Jin.

523
00:41:08,827 --> 00:41:10,827
