530
00:41:36,828 --> 00:41:42,428
If my father finds out about this much later, he will feel utterly betrayed.

531
00:41:42,428 --> 00:41:46,268
I thought it would help with Chairman Jin's health care

532
00:41:46,268 --> 00:41:48,637
if at least one of his children knew about his condition.

533
00:41:48,637 --> 00:41:50,798
I'll keep the secret.

534
00:41:50,798 --> 00:41:52,567
However,

535
00:41:54,467 --> 00:41:58,838
let me see my father.

536
00:42:00,378 --> 00:42:02,878
Now. Immediately.

537
00:42:04,451 --> 00:42:06,448
Let's do that.

538
00:42:17,498 --> 00:42:24,298
Chairman Jin's family will make a visit to the ICU.

539
00:42:30,708 --> 00:42:33,778
It's just this once.

540
00:42:33,778 --> 00:42:35,817
Let's go now.

541
00:42:35,817 --> 00:42:37,548
Let's go.

542
00:42:41,292 --> 00:42:42,887
   

543
00:42:42,887 --> 00:42:46,188
Why did you keep Father's illness to yourself?

544
00:42:46,188 --> 00:42:47,328
What were you thinking?

545
00:42:47,328 --> 00:42:49,628
I made a good pass for you to finally score.

546
00:42:49,628 --> 00:42:51,458
What's important is that we're here.

547
00:42:51,458 --> 00:42:55,127
- What is this? 
 - I thought visits were prohibited.

548
00:42:55,127 --> 00:42:57,398
Was that wrong information?

549
00:42:57,398 --> 00:43:00,668
Your family insisted on seeing Chairman Jin.

550
00:43:00,668 --> 00:43:05,747
As a doctor, do you think Father is in a state to receive visitors?

551
00:43:05,747 --> 00:43:06,807
No.

552
00:43:06,807 --> 00:43:10,048
There's a danger of infection if he sees outside visitors.

553
00:43:10,048 --> 00:43:13,418
On top of that, he absolutely must rest now.

554
00:43:13,418 --> 00:43:16,218
Hey, are you the doctor here?

555
00:43:16,218 --> 00:43:17,858
Don't step out of the line and get into this.

556
00:43:17,858 --> 00:43:22,957
I'm speaking as the chairman of Soonyang Medical Center.

557
00:43:22,957 --> 00:43:25,927
If you go against your conviction as a doctor

558
00:43:25,927 --> 00:43:28,838
and allow them to visit the ICU,

559
00:43:28,838 --> 00:43:32,608
then I will dismiss you immediately as the chairman.

560
00:43:32,608 --> 00:43:35,707
- You! 
 - If you...

561
00:43:35,707 --> 00:43:39,807
make another scene at the hospital in regard to Father,

562
00:43:39,807 --> 00:43:41,948
be ready for consequences.

563
00:43:42,817 --> 00:43:48,717
You will never get to set foot inside Soonyang Medical Center again.

564
00:43:51,117 --> 00:43:54,958
We managed to get over this, thanks to Director Jung's call.

565
00:43:55,798 --> 00:44:01,228
This family is unpredictable, so who knows when they'll barge in again?

566
00:44:01,228 --> 00:44:03,097
Thank you, Father.

567
00:44:03,097 --> 00:44:06,708
Please keep this a secret until the day of the board meeting.

568
00:44:07,645 --> 00:44:09,493
I cannot believe this.

569
00:44:09,493 --> 00:44:11,438
Our family is...

570
00:44:11,438 --> 00:44:17,147
quite ambitious, and there are many aspects that are tough for me to understand.

571
00:44:17,147 --> 00:44:20,058
However, I never thought

572
00:44:20,058 --> 00:44:24,058
they were capable of doing something so atrocious

573
00:44:24,058 --> 00:44:27,327
against your grandfather. If I had, I...

574
00:44:31,628 --> 00:44:35,168
It wasn't a car accident?

575
00:44:35,967 --> 00:44:40,667
You knew that, yet you agreed to close the police investigation?

576
00:44:40,667 --> 00:44:44,137
Well, there's a backstory.

577
00:44:44,137 --> 00:44:47,778
You said you'd make sure your family wouldn't touch Do Jun.

578
00:44:47,778 --> 00:44:50,178
Yet this is what it came down to?

579
00:44:50,178 --> 00:44:54,147
I will report to the police.

580
00:44:55,788 --> 00:44:57,618
Father...

581
00:44:59,220 --> 00:45:02,950
I was the one who insisted on stopping the investigation, Mother.

582
00:45:04,328 --> 00:45:06,128
Do Jun, it was you?

583
00:45:06,128 --> 00:45:07,668
Why?

584
00:45:09,168 --> 00:45:11,338
Because I wanted to live.

585
00:45:17,114 --> 00:45:21,407
If the culprit is one of us in the family,

586
00:45:21,407 --> 00:45:25,117
they'll be able to evade the police investigation.

587
00:45:25,117 --> 00:45:26,787
No matter whom it is,

588
00:45:26,787 --> 00:45:30,387
that person will have the money and power of Soonyang too.

589
00:45:32,927 --> 00:45:34,657
The police investigation was stopped,

590
00:45:34,657 --> 00:45:37,837
but General Manager Woo Byeong Jun has been searching.

591
00:45:37,837 --> 00:45:42,798
It won't take long to find those who planned or abetted this accident.

592
00:45:43,437 --> 00:45:47,307
So please let Grandfather have his way, Mother.

593
00:45:47,307 --> 00:45:53,208
Your grandfather is the scariest of them all and is not trustworthy.

594
00:45:55,608 --> 00:45:56,725
I know.

595
00:45:56,725 --> 00:46:03,364
But he needs me the most at this point, Mother.

596
00:46:03,364 --> 00:46:10,018
You know that Grandfather uses any ways and means to get what he wants.

597
00:46:11,598 --> 00:46:17,468
He'll do his best to keep me safe.

598
00:46:21,907 --> 00:46:26,978
Just as Do Jun says, let's give him our trust this time.

599
00:46:34,487 --> 00:46:38,817
I should at least request more bodyguards.

600
00:46:42,549 --> 00:46:44,585
You should go, Father.

601
00:47:03,648 --> 00:47:05,417
Hyeong Jun.

602
00:47:07,455 --> 00:47:10,896
Mom and Dad are gone. You should go.

603
00:47:10,896 --> 00:47:13,328
I'm here as your caregiver.

604
00:47:13,328 --> 00:47:15,657
Don't mind me.

605
00:47:15,657 --> 00:47:18,657
I'm fine. I'm not hurt in any way.

606
00:47:18,657 --> 00:47:21,027
I'm not fine.

607
00:47:21,027 --> 00:47:22,897
I'm in pain.

608
00:47:22,897 --> 00:47:24,637
What?

609
00:47:27,237 --> 00:47:29,608
You really can't take a hint.

610
00:47:29,608 --> 00:47:34,348
And you really don't care about your brother.

611
00:47:35,418 --> 00:47:37,947
My album fell through.

612
00:47:37,947 --> 00:47:39,947
Why?

613
00:47:39,947 --> 00:47:41,387
Did something happen?

614
00:47:41,387 --> 00:47:46,488
As you can see from looking at my face, I'm a singer with good looks,

615
00:47:46,488 --> 00:47:49,597
but another singer made his debut with the same image.

616
00:47:49,597 --> 00:47:51,698
He preempted my market.

617
00:47:51,698 --> 00:47:57,327
Because of him, I've totally become a bust.

618
00:47:57,967 --> 00:48:00,567
Gosh. Look at that.

619
00:48:01,637 --> 00:48:06,137
That was a charming performance.

620
00:48:11,277 --> 00:48:13,148
- Jin Do Jun. 
 - Yes?

621
00:48:13,148 --> 00:48:15,288
Come here.

622
00:48:15,288 --> 00:48:18,858
- Why? 
 - Because your brother said so.

623
00:48:20,987 --> 00:48:22,527
Yes, Sir.

624
00:48:28,268 --> 00:48:30,998
Do Jun, I'll continue to do music.

625
00:48:30,998 --> 00:48:34,168
So I'll make a fortune, too.

626
00:48:34,168 --> 00:48:35,438
Okay.

627
00:48:35,438 --> 00:48:39,937
You can have all of my money.

628
00:48:39,937 --> 00:48:41,347
What?

629
00:48:42,648 --> 00:48:47,288
Later, much later,

630
00:48:47,288 --> 00:48:50,758
when Mom and Dad leave us their inheritance,

631
00:48:50,758 --> 00:48:55,328
you can have everything, too.

632
00:48:58,598 --> 00:49:03,298
Let's not live in torment over some money.

633
00:49:04,668 --> 00:49:09,068
You can have all of my money.

634
00:49:12,107 --> 00:49:13,777
Hyeong Jun.

635
00:49:18,148 --> 00:49:25,047
So you have to give me all your money, too.

636
00:49:31,898 --> 00:49:33,268
- Let go. 
 - I can't.

637
00:49:33,268 --> 00:49:35,327
- Let go of my hand. 
 - I can't let go of your hand.

638
00:49:35,327 --> 00:49:38,268
Just take this orange.

639
00:49:38,268 --> 00:49:40,443
I thought you were cool for once.

