00:50:14,237 --> 00:50:19,937
I looked up the bank statement of the truck driver for the past year.

644
00:50:20,978 --> 00:50:22,447
It's just as we expected.

645
00:50:22,447 --> 00:50:28,148
He didn't receive a huge amount through his bank, or anything else in particular.

646
00:50:28,148 --> 00:50:32,788
Even if the instigator paid him, I'm sure it was in cash.

647
00:50:33,728 --> 00:50:35,458
What about the call history?

648
00:50:35,458 --> 00:50:38,298
 The frequency of the last number he called on the day  

