00:50:38,298 --> 00:50:41,409
of the accident sharply rose in the past month.

650
00:50:41,409 --> 00:50:43,625
I have investigated that as well.

651
00:50:43,625 --> 00:50:45,907
It was a burner phone.

652
00:50:45,907 --> 00:50:50,337
I also found out that the truck driver was an ex-convict.

653
00:50:50,337 --> 00:50:52,137
He was charged for gambling.

