00:56:10,898 --> 00:56:12,228
We're closing the office as of today.

738
00:56:12,228 --> 00:56:15,568
You're all on a break until you get further notice. Move!

739
00:56:29,618 --> 00:56:30,878
Who are you?

740
00:56:30,878 --> 00:56:33,348
Who are you people?

741
00:56:33,348 --> 00:56:36,217
The accident on the outer road of Incheon.

742
00:56:36,217 --> 00:56:40,458
Did you plan and abet the accident in this office?

743
00:56:40,458 --> 00:56:41,628
What is this nonsense...

744
00:56:41,628 --> 00:56:45,328
You knew there were no CCTVs on the site of the accident.

745
00:56:45,328 --> 00:56:50,568
An ordinary intersection in Korea would have a CCTV in that region,

746
00:56:50,568 --> 00:56:55,637
but a civil servant made a mistake and left it out as an exception.

747
00:56:55,637 --> 00:56:58,338
If you're aware of that, you're either with the police,

748
00:56:58,338 --> 00:57:01,878
or the person who planned the accident.

749
00:57:03,578 --> 00:57:06,748
Who's behind you?

750
00:57:09,617 --> 00:57:13,217
How did he meet with the instigator of the accident?

751
00:57:19,357 --> 00:57:24,168
 He was given instructions and paid by using coin lockers. 

752
00:57:35,377 --> 00:57:37,418
There are no traces of transactions for antique artworks.

753
00:57:37,418 --> 00:57:40,188
