754
00:57:40,188 --> 00:57:42,118
Whoever this is

755
00:57:42,118 --> 00:57:48,087
has a knack for hiding the source of the fund.

756
00:58:05,077 --> 00:58:06,954
I never imagined I would face a day

757
00:58:06,954 --> 00:58:11,555
