758
00:58:13,717 --> 00:58:16,688
This is interesting.

759
00:58:16,688 --> 00:58:19,958
Nobody used to pay any attention to folk paintings like these,

760
00:58:19,958 --> 00:58:26,628
but they rose to value like this thanks to you, CEO Mo, a savvy investor.

761
00:58:35,737 --> 00:58:38,957
I hear you're highly interested in paintings with flowers and birds.

762
00:58:43,918 --> 00:58:47,717
This is one of your collections, right?

763
00:58:47,717 --> 00:58:49,248
A painting of flowers and birds is made

764
00:58:49,248 --> 00:58:54,962
hoping that the flowers and birds will bring the family longevity, blessings, and love.

765
00:58:54,962 --> 00:58:58,298
I especially loved the bold colors,

766
00:58:58,298 --> 00:59:03,628
and lively theme for this painting, so this is my most cherished possession.

767
00:59:05,367 --> 00:59:10,207
If this is the gallery's collection, it must be in the storage.

768
00:59:10,978 --> 00:59:12,338
What is it?

769
00:59:12,338 --> 00:59:15,678
I came upon a situation that this painting

770
00:59:15,678 --> 00:59:18,447
