00:59:19,918 --> 00:59:22,987
I received a report that murder instigators,

773
00:59:22,987 --> 00:59:27,657
who disguised it as a car accident, paid the price with this painting.

774
00:59:29,287 --> 00:59:33,728
May I check and see if this painting is here?

